{"tid":87504,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傷心山神IG透去意？","createTime":"2017-01-20T01:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T01:34:01.000Z","uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58e2ce07f3134c76128caf23ad6b58783d61965a","tid":87504,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:13:40.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=237486d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴球星阿歷斯山齊士在Instagram透露離心，暗示自己心已碎。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴球星阿歷斯山齊士（Alexis Sanchez）最近接連在比賽時流露出沮喪、傷感的表情和動作，令人擔心他是否已意興闌珊，決心要離開阿仙奴？這位智利前鋒剛在Instagram用文字表明心跡，寫下「心碎」、「閉門哭泣」、「孤獨作戰」等字眼，看來阿仙奴領隊雲加不得不作好最壞打算。<br />\n<br />\n山齊士在Instagram上載自己在操練中大笑相片，並寫上：「堅強的人都有一顆破碎的心，他們關上門偷泣，默默地獨自戰鬥。」<br />\n<br />\n他的意思很明顯，以堅強的人形容自己，對於球隊的續約問題和成績都感到心碎，但他仍然默默戰鬥，獨自撐起球隊。山齊士今季仍以14個入波，與車路士的迪亞高哥斯達和曼聯的伊巴謙莫域並列頭號射手。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : 互聯網"},{"pid":"a6561ee6afed33eb96e3464007b10e1f55666909","tid":87504,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:15:11.000Z","msg":"山狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3312d4d32696a4004f58c968eb1902f898641cd1","tid":87504,"uid":2316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:20:23.000Z","msg":"讚緊雲加姐"},{"pid":"7fd934eef54ae7096611c85e711ac1f07c43246a","tid":87504,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:22:16.000Z","msg":"擺明見到雲加偷喊啦"},{"pid":"cd3256e745b2b4e079eb2ef80600e85256229e6e","tid":87504,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:23:01.000Z","msg":"MK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b2dcf683c4b3f2bf8f1301a5c2bd9eded454bb","tid":87504,"uid":33441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:24:54.000Z","msg":"跳草裙舞扭加人工是常識吧"},{"pid":"fec55dc3210d8ce43e738dff6d1081058b771a9c","tid":87504,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:24:56.000Z","msg":"收皮啦山狗"},{"pid":"6f27f32b055f855cfd1422159e3f3f391766e05a","tid":87504,"uid":3307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:26:21.000Z","msg":"乜鳩翻譯唻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb6adf8367e10815b95d6e6745a2964a18e7ddc","tid":87504,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:30:13.000Z","msg":"懷念爺爺"},{"pid":"e50bfd666e63d457ebb372c58ff77bc0dc193b5e","tid":87504,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T01:34:01.000Z","msg":"take care<br />\nbe strong"}]}